title: Food Matters.avi.avi
description:
Food Matters - You Are What You Eat

   Pharmacology Productions - A film by James Colquhoun and Laurentine Ten Bosch
   Food matters is a hard hitting, fast paced look at our current state of health.  Despite the billions of dollars of funding and research into new "so called" cures we continue to suffer from a raft of chronic ills and 
   everyday maladies.  Patching up an over toxic and  overindulgent population with a host of toxic therapies and nutrient-sparse food is definitely not helping the situation.
   Join the world&#039;s leading authorities on nutrition and natural healing as they uncover the true causes of diseases.
   Find out what works and what does not and what is killing you.
   Become informed about the choices you have for you ad your family&#039;s health that could save your life.
   Foodmatters sets about uncovering the trillion dollar worldwide "Sickness Industry" and exposes a growing body of scientific evidence proving that nutritional therapy can be more effective, more economical and less harmful as well as less invasive than most conventional medical treatments.  Film personally reviewed by Al. Vero . 
AVI windows media player format
   Ripped by B.K. Schmendrick
